# NSKeyedArchiveRootObjectKey

**Global Variable**

Archives created using the class method [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSKeyedArchiver/archivedData(withRootObject:)] use this key for the root object in the hierarchy of encoded objects. The [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSKeyedUnarchiver] class method [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/NSKeyedUnarchiver/unarchiveObject(with:)] looks for this root key as well.

## Declaration

```swift
let NSKeyedArchiveRootObjectKey: String
```
